ng&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;5GZEcx&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;华硕 ROG Ally X 评测：最好的 Windows 游戏手持设备&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24204770/asus-rog-ally- x-review-handheld-gaming-pc&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;XYN8Dp&quot;>;配备 16GB 7500 MT/s 内存和 50 瓦时电池，它比原始 Ally 的 6400 MT/s 内存领先一步......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235413/acer- nitro-blaze-7-handheld-gaming-pc-specs&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235413/acer-nitro-blaze-7-handheld-gaming-pc-specs" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235413/acer-nitro-blaze-7-handheld-gaming-pc-specs</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-04T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-04T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> GoPro 的新旗舰 Hero 13 Black 获得关键升级和广泛的镜头</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;GoPro Hero 13 Black 的图片及附件。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/kIgBKTi_btl-onxq23QuXnPj1mM=/24x0:2027x1335/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73562878/GoPro_Hero_13_Black.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;带有一些附件的 GoPro Hero 13 Black。&lt;/em>; |图片：GoPro&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;wok7A7&quot;>;GoPro 有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://investor.gopro.com/press-releases/press-release-details/2024/GoPro-宣布两款新相机-The-399-HERO13-Black-and-the-199-HERO/default.aspx&quot;>;宣布&lt;/a>;两款新运动相机，&lt;a href=&quot;https://go .redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fgopro.com%2Fen%2Fus%2Fshop%2Fcameras%2Flearn%2Fhero13black%2FCHDHX-131-master.html&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp; ;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F4%2F24235177%2Fgopro-hero-13-black-10-bit-g-log-upgraded-battery-new-lenses&quot; rel=&quot;赞助的 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;GoPro Hero 13 Black&lt;/a>; 和较小的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A% 2F%2Fgopro.com%2Fen%2Fus%2Fshop%2Fcameras%2Flearn%2Fhero%2FCHDHF-131-master.html&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9% 2F4%2F24235177%2Fgopro-hero-13-black-10-bit-g-log-upgraded-battery-new-lenses&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;GoPro Hero&lt;/a>;。 Hero 13 Black 售价 399 美元，Hero 售价 199 美元。两款产品现已接受预订，并将分别于 9 月 10 日和 9 月 22 日发布。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;JK4mK4&quot;>;GoPro 为 13 Black 添加的一些新功能包括磁性安装和充电、三个新镜头和重新设计的电池，该公司称其容量比前身高出 10%。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;C4zF4i&quot;>; &lt;!-- ######## 开始批量视频 ######## -->;&lt;div data-analytics-viewport=&quot;video&quot; data -analytics-action=&quot;volume:view:article:middle&quot; data-analytics-label=&quot;GoPro Hero 13|117709&quot; data-volume-uuid=&quot;08bf58f61&quot; data-volume-id=&quot;117709&quot; data-analytics-placement =&quot;article:middle&quot; data-volume-placement=&quot;article&quot; data-volume-autoplay=&quot;false&quot; id=&quot;volume-placement-14&quot; class=&quot;volume-video&quot;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;!-- # ####### END VOLUME VIDEO ######## -->; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;2H7Mvp&quot;>;Hero 13 Black 具有机内降噪功能，可录制 HLG HDR 视频和 G-Log 中的 10 位视频。它还支持新的连拍慢动作模式，可以以每秒 400 帧的速度录制 720p 视频、以 360fps 的速度录制 900p 视频、以 120fps 的速度录制 5.3K 视频。相机还...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235177/gopro-hero-13-black-10-bit-g- log-upgraded-battery-new-lenses&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235177/gopro-hero-13-black-10-bit-g-log-upgraded-battery-new-lenses" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235177/gopro-hero-13-black-10-bit-g-log-upgraded-battery-new-lenses</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-04T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-04T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Zillow 升级版人工智能搜索将向您展示更多买不起的房屋</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;展示 Zillow 中新的 AI 搜索功能的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/42hmgyfBiCWGDcqFv7LLVQbm50U=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn .com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73562853/zillow_ai_search.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Zillow&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;GU7NnP&quot;>;Zillow 是 &lt;a href=&quot;https: //zillow.mediaroom.com/2024-09-04-Zillows-AI-powered-home-search-gets-smarter-with-new-natural-language-features&quot;>;升级其人工智能搜索功能&lt;/a>;能够根据距您的办公室、学校或其他兴趣点的距离查找房屋或出租房屋。现在，您无需通过选择特定位置或过滤器来缩小搜索范围，只需输入“距千禧公园 30 分钟车程的房屋”即可。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;arlfEZ&quot;>;这对于像我这样的人来说非常方便。我总是在不熟悉的地方寻找梦想家园，现在我将能够搜索“迪士尼世界附近的家园”，而不是在整个奥兰多撒下一张大网。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;bNWDXQ&quot;>;Zillow 还可以让您根据负担能力搜索要购买或租赁的房屋，例如“西雅图每月低于 4,000 美元的房屋”。 Zillow &lt;a href=&quot;https://zillow.mediaroom.com/2023-01-26-Zillows-new-AI-powered-natural-language-search-is-a-first-in-real-estate&quot;>;第一个去年推出了人工智能搜索&lt;/a>;，让您可以...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235154/zillow-chatbot -home-search-commute&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235154/zillow-chatbot-home-search-commute" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235154/zillow-chatbot-home-search-commute</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-04T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-04T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> 《塞尔达传说：智慧的回声》上手体验：实验时代仍在继续</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个穿着裙子的女孩，头上举着一根发光的棒。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nXfRNJQ_fzrfuvcQAlmHipOUHe0=/747x289:2133x1213/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73562869/Screen_Shot_2024_08_30_at_5.28。 36_PM.0.png &quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：任天堂&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &